#####################################################################
#
# Configuration & common formulas
#
############################################################

#####################################################################
##
## Configuration parameters
##
CFG:
   CPAR:
        P0  = MATH_STAT
        P1  = MATH_ERRC
        P2  = MATH_CFGS
        P3  = MATH_PRIO
        P4  = MATH_LOGF
        P5  = MATH_FLEN
        P6  = MATH_LOGC
        P7  = MATH_LOGM
        P8  = MATH_CHKT
        P9  = MATH_ESEQ
        P10 = MATH_CNAM
        P11 = MATH_DBUG

  STAT = P0
  ERRC = P1
  CFGS = P2
  PRIO = P3
  LOGF = P4
  FLEN = P5
  LOGC = P6
  LOGM = P7
  CHKT = P8
  ESEQ = P9
  CNAM = P10
  DBUG = P11


#//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

#####################################################################
##
## Year2000 handling.
##
OBJ: Year2000
     CPAR:
         P0 = OprClkInpYear
     CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
         P0 = OprClkInpYear
         P1 = OprClkYear
     OFV0: P1 = IF P0<1900 : P1;ELSE P0-1900;

OBJ: Fi_SetPLCClocks
     CPAR:
         P0  = OprClkControl
         P1  = OprClkDayOfWeek
         P2  = OprClkMonth
         P3  = OprClkDay
         P4  = OprClkYear
         P5  = OprClkHour
         P6  = OprClkMin
         P7  = OprClkSec
     #CFV: IF P0 == 2048 : Q1;ELSE Q0;
     CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
    # Operator tags
         P0  = OprClkControl
         P1  = OprClkDayOfWeek
         P2  = OprClkMonth
         P3  = OprClkDay
         P4  = OprClkYear
         P5  = OprClkHour
         P6  = OprClkMin
         P7  = OprClkSec
    # PLC
         P8  = Fi_WrtClkControl
         P9  = Fi_WrtClkDayOfWeek
         P10 = Fi_WrtClkMonth
         P11 = Fi_WrtClkDay
         P12 = Fi_WrtClkYear
         P13 = Fi_WrtClkHour
         P14 = Fi_WrtClkMin
         P15 = Fi_WrtClkSec
     # PLC
     OFV0:  P9  = IF S1 : P1+1; ELSE ;
     OFV1:  P10 = IF S2 : P2; ELSE ;
     OFV2:  P11 = IF S3 : P3; ELSE ;
     OFV3:  P12 = IF S4 : P4; ELSE ;
     OFV4:  P13 = IF S5 : P5; ELSE ;
     OFV5:  P14 = IF S6 : P6; ELSE ;
     OFV6:  P15 = IF S7 : P7; ELSE ;
     OFV7:  P8  = IF S0 : P0; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi2_SetPLCClocks
     CPAR:
         P0  = OprClkControl
         P1  = OprClkDayOfWeek
         P2  = OprClkMonth
         P3  = OprClkDay
         P4  = OprClkYear
         P5  = OprClkHour
         P6  = OprClkMin
         P7  = OprClkSec
     #CFV: IF P0 == 2048 : Q1;ELSE Q0;
     CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
    # Operator tags
         P0  = OprClkControl
         P1  = OprClkDayOfWeek
         P2  = OprClkMonth
         P3  = OprClkDay
         P4  = OprClkYear
         P5  = OprClkHour
         P6  = OprClkMin
         P7  = OprClkSec
    # PLC
         P8  = Fi2_WrtClkControl
         P9  = Fi2_WrtClkDayOfWeek
         P10 = Fi2_WrtClkMonth
         P11 = Fi2_WrtClkDay
         P12 = Fi2_WrtClkYear
         P13 = Fi2_WrtClkHour
         P14 = Fi2_WrtClkMin
         P15 = Fi2_WrtClkSec
     # PLC
     OFV0:  P9  = IF S1 : P1+1; ELSE ;
     OFV1:  P10 = IF S2 : P2; ELSE ;
     OFV2:  P11 = IF S3 : P3; ELSE ;
     OFV3:  P12 = IF S4 : P4; ELSE ;
     OFV4:  P13 = IF S5 : P5; ELSE ;
     OFV5:  P14 = IF S6 : P6; ELSE ;
     OFV6:  P15 = IF S7 : P7; ELSE ;
     OFV7:  P8  = IF S0 : P0; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi3_SetPLCClocks
     CPAR:
         P0  = OprClkControl
         P1  = OprClkDayOfWeek
         P2  = OprClkMonth
         P3  = OprClkDay
         P4  = OprClkYear
         P5  = OprClkHour
         P6  = OprClkMin
         P7  = OprClkSec
     #CFV: IF P0 == 2048 : Q1;ELSE Q0;
     CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
    # Operator tags
         P0  = OprClkControl
         P1  = OprClkDayOfWeek
         P2  = OprClkMonth
         P3  = OprClkDay
         P4  = OprClkYear
         P5  = OprClkHour
         P6  = OprClkMin
         P7  = OprClkSec
    # PLC
         P8  = Fi3_WrtClkControl
         P9  = Fi3_WrtClkDayOfWeek
         P10 = Fi3_WrtClkMonth
         P11 = Fi3_WrtClkDay
         P12 = Fi3_WrtClkYear
         P13 = Fi3_WrtClkHour
         P14 = Fi3_WrtClkMin
         P15 = Fi3_WrtClkSec
     # PLC
     OFV0:  P9  = IF S1 : P1+1; ELSE ;
     OFV1:  P10 = IF S2 : P2; ELSE ;
     OFV2:  P11 = IF S3 : P3; ELSE ;
     OFV3:  P12 = IF S4 : P4; ELSE ;
     OFV4:  P13 = IF S5 : P5; ELSE ;
     OFV5:  P14 = IF S6 : P6; ELSE ;
     OFV6:  P15 = IF S7 : P7; ELSE ;
     OFV7:  P8  = IF S0 : P0; ELSE ;


OBJ: Fi_CopyClock
     CPAR:
   P0 = Fi_PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P1 = Fi_PLCClkMonth
   P2 = Fi_PLCClkDay
   P3 = Fi_PLCClkYear
   P4 = Fi_PLCClkHour
   P5 = Fi_PLCClkMin
   P6 = Fi_PLCClkSec
   P7 = Fi_PLCClkSet
   P8 = Fi_PLC_CommOK
     CFV: IF P8 && !(S8&3): Q1; ELSE Q0;
     OPAR:
   P0  = Fi_PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P1  = Fi_PLCClkMonth
   P2  = Fi_PLCClkDay
   P3  = Fi_PLCClkYear
   P4  = Fi_PLCClkHour
   P5  = Fi_PLCClkMin
   P6  = Fi_PLCClkSec
   P7  = Fi_PLCClkSet
   P8  = PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P9  = PLCClkMonth
   P10 = PLCClkDay
   P11 = PLCClkYear
   P12 = PLCClkHour
   P13 = PLCClkMin
   P14 = PLCClkSec
   P15 = CLK_TSET
     OFV0:  P8  = ELSE P0;
     OFV1:  P9  = ELSE P1;
     OFV2:  P10 = ELSE P2;
     OFV3:  P11 = ELSE P3;
     OFV4:  P12 = ELSE P4;
     OFV5:  P13 = ELSE P5;
     OFV6:  P14 = ELSE P6;
     OFV7:  P15 = IF (P0!=0) && (P1!=0) && (P2!=0) && (S7==3) : P7; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi2_CopyClock
     CPAR:
   P0 = Fi2_PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P1 = Fi2_PLCClkMonth
   P2 = Fi2_PLCClkDay
   P3 = Fi2_PLCClkYear
   P4 = Fi2_PLCClkHour
   P5 = Fi2_PLCClkMin
   P6 = Fi2_PLCClkSec
   P7 = Fi2_PLCClkSet
   P8 = Fi_PLC_CommOK
   P9 = Fi2_PLC_CommOK
     CFV: IF !P8 && !(S8&3) && P9 && !(S9&3): Q1; ELSE Q0;
     OPAR:
   P0  = Fi2_PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P1  = Fi2_PLCClkMonth
   P2  = Fi2_PLCClkDay
   P3  = Fi2_PLCClkYear
   P4  = Fi2_PLCClkHour
   P5  = Fi2_PLCClkMin
   P6  = Fi2_PLCClkSec
   P7  = Fi2_PLCClkSet
   P8  = PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P9  = PLCClkMonth
   P10 = PLCClkDay
   P11 = PLCClkYear
   P12 = PLCClkHour
   P13 = PLCClkMin
   P14 = PLCClkSec
   P15 = CLK_TSET
     OFV0:  P8  = ELSE P0;
     OFV1:  P9  = ELSE P1;
     OFV2:  P10 = ELSE P2;
     OFV3:  P11 = ELSE P3;
     OFV4:  P12 = ELSE P4;
     OFV5:  P13 = ELSE P5;
     OFV6:  P14 = ELSE P6;
     OFV7:  P15 = IF (P0!=0) && (P1!=0) && (P2!=0) && (S7==3) : P7; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi3_CopyClock
     CPAR:
   P0 = Fi3_PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P1 = Fi3_PLCClkMonth
   P2 = Fi3_PLCClkDay
   P3 = Fi3_PLCClkYear
   P4 = Fi3_PLCClkHour
   P5 = Fi3_PLCClkMin
   P6 = Fi3_PLCClkSec
   P7 = Fi3_PLCClkSet
   P8 = Fi_PLC_CommOK
   P9 = Fi2_PLC_CommOK
   P10= Fi3_PLC_CommOK
     CFV: IF !P8 && !(S8&3) && !P9 && !(S9&3) && P10 && !(S10&3): Q1; ELSE Q0;
     OPAR:
   P0  = Fi3_PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P1  = Fi3_PLCClkMonth
   P2  = Fi3_PLCClkDay
   P3  = Fi3_PLCClkYear
   P4  = Fi3_PLCClkHour
   P5  = Fi3_PLCClkMin
   P6  = Fi3_PLCClkSec
   P7  = Fi3_PLCClkSet
   P8  = PLCClkDayOfWeek
   P9  = PLCClkMonth
   P10 = PLCClkDay
   P11 = PLCClkYear
   P12 = PLCClkHour
   P13 = PLCClkMin
   P14 = PLCClkSec
   P15 = CLK_TSET
     OFV0:  P8  = ELSE P0;
     OFV1:  P9  = ELSE P1;
     OFV2:  P10 = ELSE P2;
     OFV3:  P11 = ELSE P3;
     OFV4:  P12 = ELSE P4;
     OFV5:  P13 = ELSE P5;
     OFV6:  P14 = ELSE P6;
     OFV7:  P15 = IF (P0!=0) && (P1!=0) && (P2!=0) && (S7==3) : P7; ELSE ;


# Syncronize PC to clock to PLC clock if Difference > 2s
# Convert Daily time to seconds and compare it

OBJ: PCClockSync
     CPAR:
   P0 = PLCClkMonth
   P1 = PLCClkDay
   P2 = PLCClkYear
   P3 = PLCClkHour
   P4 = PLCClkMin
   P5 = PLCClkSec
     CFV: IF (P0!=0) && (P1!=0) && (S5 == 3) : Q1; ELSE Q0;
     OPAR:
   P0  = PLCClkMonth
   P1  = PLCClkDay
   P2  = PLCClkYear
   P3  = PLCClkHour
   P4  = PLCClkMin
   P5  = PLCClkSec
   P6  = SysClkMonth
   P7  = SysClkDay
   P8  = SysClkYear
   P9  = SysClkHour
   P10 = SysClkMin
   P11 = SysClkSec
   P12 = CLK_TSET
     # If (10 < DailyPLCTimeInSec < (86400-10)) and PLCDate!=PCDate then Set PC Time
     OFV0:  P12  = IF ((10 < (P3*60+P4)*60+P5) && ((P3*60+P4)*60+P5 < (86400-10))) && \
                ((P0!=P6) || (P1!=P7) || ((ABS(P2-P8)!=0) && ((ABS(P2-P8)!=100)))) : 1; ELSE ;
     # If (PLCDate==PCDate) and (10 < DailyPLCTimeInSec < (86400-10)) and
     #          (ABS(DailyPLCTimeInSec-DailyPCTimeInSec)>3) then Set PC Time
     OFV1:  P12  = IF ((P0==P6) && (P1==P7) && ((ABS(P2-P8)==0) || ((ABS(P2-P8)==100)))) && \
                ((10 < (P3*60+P4)*60+P5) && ((P3*60+P4)*60+P5 < (86400-10))) && \
                ( ABS( ((P3*60+P4)*60+P5) - ((P9*60+P10)*60+P11) ) > 2) : 1; ELSE ;

##//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////


####################################################################
#
# Writing the system start flag
#
OBJ: SystemStart
     CPAR:
        P0 = ARCH_SRV_STAT
     CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
        P0 = SystemStart
        P1 = ARCH_SRV_STAT
     OFV0: P0 = IF P1 : 1; ELSE ;

## Set MBT_PRIO to 14 if MBTCP started or MBT_PRIO==19

#####################################################################
##
## MODBUS+, MBTCP, TIMER restart
##
OBJ: MBPTaskStop
    CPAR:
        P0 = CLK_DIFF
    CFV: IF (P0<-30 || P0>300) : Q1;ELSE Q0;
    OPAR:
       P0= Task_Restart01
       P1= MBPLUS_SRV_LNCH
       P2= MBPLUS_SRV_STAT
    # If any MB+ is running must be stopped when the clock is
    # changed backwards more than 30 seconds or forward more than 5 minutes
    OFV0: P1 = IF P2 : 0;ELSE;
    OFV1: P0 = IF P2 : 1;ELSE;

OBJ: MBPTaskStart
    CPAR:
       P0 = MBPLUS_SRV_STAT
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
       P0 = Task_Restart01
       P1 = MBPLUS_SRV_LNCH
    OFV0: P1 = IF P0 && !P1: 1; ELSE;
    OFV1: P0 = ELSE 0;

OBJ: MBTTaskStop
    CPAR:
        P0 = CLK_DIFF
    CFV: IF (P0<-30 || P0>300) : Q1;ELSE Q0;
    OPAR:
       P0= Task_Restart02
       P1= MBTCP_SRV_LNCH
       P2= MBTCP_SRV_STAT
    # If any MB+ is running must be stopped when the clock is
    # changed backwards more than 30 seconds or forward more than 5 minutes
    OFV0: P1 = IF P2 : 0;ELSE;
    OFV1: P0 = IF P2 : 1;ELSE;

OBJ: MBTTaskStart
    CPAR:
       P0 = MBTCP_SRV_STAT
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
       P0 = Task_Restart02
       P1 = MBTCP_SRV_LNCH
    OFV0: P1 = IF P0 && !P1: 1; ELSE;
    OFV1: P0 = ELSE 0;

OBJ: TimerTaskStop
    CPAR:
        P0 = CLK_DIFF
    CFV: IF (P0<-30 || P0>300) : Q1;ELSE Q0;
    OPAR:
       P0= Task_Restart03
       P1= TIM_SRV_LNCH
       P2= TIM_SRV_STAT
    OFV0: P1 = IF P2 : 0;ELSE;
    OFV1: P0 = IF P2 : 1;ELSE;

OBJ: TimerTaskStart
    CPAR:
       P0 = TIM_SRV_STAT
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
       P0 = Task_Restart03
       P1 = TIM_SRV_LNCH
    OFV0: P1 = IF P0 && !P1: 1; ELSE;
    OFV1: P0 = ELSE 0;


##########################################################################
#
# START/STOP Monitor on other node
#
OBJ: MON1_START
   CPAR:
      P0 = MON1_START
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = MON1_START
      P1 = MON1_SRV_LNCH
      P2 = EVVI1_SRV_LNCH
   OFV0:   P1 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;
   OFV1:   P2 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;

OBJ: MON2_START
   CPAR:
      P0 = MON2_START
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = MON2_START
      P1 = MON2_SRV_LNCH
      P2 = EVVI2_SRV_LNCH
   OFV0:   P1 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;
   OFV1:   P2 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;

OBJ: MON3_START
   CPAR:
      P0 = MON3_START
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = MON3_START
      P1 = MON3_SRV_LNCH
      P2 = EVVI3_SRV_LNCH
   OFV0:   P1 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;
   OFV1:   P2 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;

OBJ: MON4_START
   CPAR:
      P0 = MON4_START
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = MON4_START
      P1 = MON4_SRV_LNCH
      P2 = EVVI4_SRV_LNCH
   OFV0:   P1 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;
   OFV1:   P2 = IF P0 == 1 : 1; IF P0 == 2 : 0; ELSE;

#####################################################################
##
## Mark/unmark the tables
##
OBJ: LoggerTableSelect
    CPAR:
        P0 = T_LoggerGlbSet
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
        P0 = T_LoggerGlbSet
        P1 = T_Tbl01Selected
        P2 = T_Tbl02Selected
        P3 = T_Tbl03Selected
        P4 = T_Tbl04Selected
        P5 = T_Tbl05Selected
        P6 = T_Tbl06Selected
        P7 = T_Tbl07Selected
        P8 = T_Tbl08Selected
        P9 = T_Tbl09Selected
        P10= T_Tbl10Selected
        P11= T_Tbl11Selected
        P12= T_Tbl12Selected
        P13= T_Tbl13Selected
        P14= T_Tbl14Selected
        P15= T_Tbl15Selected
        P16= T_Tbl16Selected
        P17= T_Tbl17Selected
        P18= T_Tbl18Selected
        P19= T_Tbl19Selected
        P20= T_Tbl20Selected
        P21= T_Tbl21Selected
        P22= T_Tbl22Selected
        P23= T_Tbl23Selected
        P24= T_Tbl24Selected
        P25= T_Tbl25Selected
        P26= T_Tbl26Selected
        P27= T_Tbl27Selected
        P28= T_Tbl28Selected
        P29= T_Tbl29Selected
        P30= T_Tbl30Selected
  OFV0: P1 = ELSE P0;
  OFV1: P2 = ELSE P0;
  OFV2: P3 = ELSE P0;
  OFV3: P4 = ELSE P0;
  OFV4: P5 = ELSE P0;
  OFV5: P6 = ELSE P0;
  OFV6: P7 = ELSE P0;
  OFV7: P8 = ELSE P0;
  OFV8: P9 = ELSE P0;
  OFV9: P10= ELSE P0;
  OFV10: P11= ELSE P0;
  OFV11: P12= ELSE P0;
  OFV12: P13= ELSE P0;
  OFV13: P14= ELSE P0;
  OFV14: P15= ELSE P0;
  OFV15: P16= ELSE P0;
  OFV16: P17= ELSE P0;
  OFV17: P18= ELSE P0;
  OFV18: P19= ELSE P0;
  OFV19: P20= ELSE P0;
  OFV20: P21= ELSE P0;
  OFV21: P22= ELSE P0;
  OFV22: P23= ELSE P0;
  OFV23: P24= ELSE P0;
  OFV24: P25= ELSE P0;
  OFV25: P26= ELSE P0;
  OFV26: P27= ELSE P0;
  OFV27: P28= ELSE P0;
  OFV28: P29= ELSE P0;
  OFV29: P30= ELSE P0;


#####################################################################
##
## Setting the day selector
## If the day selector is 0, it will be set to -1
##
OBJ: LoggerDaySelector
    CPAR:
        P0  = T_Abs01Day
        P1  = T_Abs02Day
        P2  = T_Abs03Day
        P3  = T_Abs04Day
        P4  = T_Abs05Day
        P5  = T_Abs06Day
        P6  = T_Abs07Day
        P7  = T_Abs08Day
        P8  = T_Abs09Day
        P9  = T_Abs10Day
        P10 = T_Tbl01StartDay
        P11 = T_Tbl02StartDay
        P12 = T_Tbl03StartDay
        P13 = T_Tbl04StartDay
        P14 = T_Tbl05StartDay
        P15 = T_Tbl06StartDay
        P16 = T_Tbl07StartDay
        P17 = T_Tbl08StartDay
        P18 = T_Tbl09StartDay
        P19 = T_Tbl10StartDay
        P20 = T_Tbl11StartDay
        P21 = T_Tbl12StartDay
        P22 = T_Tbl13StartDay
        P23 = T_Tbl14StartDay
        P24 = T_Tbl15StartDay
        P25 = T_Tbl16StartDay
        P26 = T_Tbl17StartDay
        P27 = T_Tbl18StartDay
        P28 = T_Tbl19StartDay
        P29 = T_Tbl20StartDay
        P30 = T_Tbl21StartDay
        P31 = T_Tbl22StartDay
        P32 = T_Tbl23StartDay
        P33 = T_Tbl24StartDay
        P34 = T_Tbl25StartDay
        P35 = T_Tbl26StartDay
        P36 = T_Tbl27StartDay
        P37 = T_Tbl28StartDay
        P38 = T_Tbl29StartDay
        P39 = T_Tbl30StartDay
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
     OPAR:
        P0  = T_Abs01Day
        P1  = T_Abs02Day
        P2  = T_Abs03Day
        P3  = T_Abs04Day
        P4  = T_Abs05Day
        P5  = T_Abs06Day
        P6  = T_Abs07Day
        P7  = T_Abs08Day
        P8  = T_Abs09Day
        P9  = T_Abs10Day
        P10 = T_Tbl01StartDay
        P11 = T_Tbl02StartDay
        P12 = T_Tbl03StartDay
        P13 = T_Tbl04StartDay
        P14 = T_Tbl05StartDay
        P15 = T_Tbl06StartDay
        P16 = T_Tbl07StartDay
        P17 = T_Tbl08StartDay
        P18 = T_Tbl09StartDay
        P19 = T_Tbl10StartDay
        P20 = T_Tbl11StartDay
        P21 = T_Tbl12StartDay
        P22 = T_Tbl13StartDay
        P23 = T_Tbl14StartDay
        P24 = T_Tbl15StartDay
        P25 = T_Tbl16StartDay
        P26 = T_Tbl17StartDay
        P27 = T_Tbl18StartDay
        P28 = T_Tbl19StartDay
        P29 = T_Tbl20StartDay
        P30 = T_Tbl21StartDay
        P31 = T_Tbl22StartDay

############ If PLCLive signal for channel is not changing in 20s
#   MBT_Chxx_OK->0 :
#   Communication with PLC wrong for that channel
#

OBJ: MBT_CH01_OK
	 CPAR:
			P0 = SysClkSec
	 CFV:   IF (S0 & 3) && ( P0 % 20 == 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
			P0 = MBT_CH01_Live
			P1 = MBT_CH01_OK
			P2 = MBT_CH01_LiveS
	 OFV0:  P1 = IF (P0 == P2) : 1; ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:  P2 = IF (P2 == 0) : 1; IF (P0<10000) : P0+1; ELSE 1;

			P2 = MBT_CH36_LiveS

###############################################################################
#
#/@ (Fi_xx)
#
##############################################################################


OBJ: Fi_PLC_Popup_01
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi_AStEvMs212
   CFV:  IF S0&3 : Q1; ELSE Q0;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Popup_01
      P1 = Fi_AStEvMs212
   OFV0:   P0 = ELSE P1;


OBJ: Fi_PLC_Popup_07
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi_AStEvMs218
   CFV:  IF S0&3 : Q1; ELSE Q0;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Popup_07
      P1 = Fi_AStEvMs218
   OFV0:   P0 = ELSE P1;




############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is written but not changed MB1_PLCOK->0 #######
#/@  Communication may be OK but MB1_PLC is not running
#
OBJ: Fi_MB1_PLCOK
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi_MB1_PLCLive
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Fi_MB1_PLCLive
      P1 = Fi_MB1_PLCOK
   OFV0:   P1 = IF (S0 & 3) == 3 : 1; IF S0 : 0; ELSE;


############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is not changing in 10 s MB1_PLC_CommOK->0 #######
#   Communication with MB1_PLC wrong
#
OBJ: Fi_MB1_PLC_CommOK
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 10)== 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB1_PLCLive
                P1 = Fi_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi_MB1_PLCLivePrev
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 != P2) : 1;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = ELSE P0;



############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is written but not changed MB1_PLCOK->0 #######
#/@  Communication may be OK but MB1_PLC is not running
#
OBJ: Fi_MB2_PLCOK
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi_MB2_PLCLive
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Fi_MB2_PLCLive
      P1 = Fi_MB2_PLCOK
   OFV0:   P1 = IF (S0 & 3) == 3 : 1; IF S0 : 0; ELSE;


############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is not changing in 10 s MB1_PLC_CommOK->0 #######
#   Communication with MB1_PLC wrong
#
OBJ: Fi_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 10)== 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB2_PLCLive
                P1 = Fi_MB2_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi_MB2_PLCLivePrev
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 != P2) : 1;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = ELSE P0;




############ MB channel failover #######
#
OBJ: Fi_MB_FailOver
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 4)== 1) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 OFV0:   P0 = IF P1 && (P0 == -1 || P0 == -2 || P0 == 1) : 1;  IF P2 && (P0 == -1 || P0 == -2 || P0 == 2) : 2;  IF !P1 && (P0 == 1) : -2;  IF !P2 && (P0 == 2) : -1;  ELSE;
	 OFV1:   P0 = IF P0 == 0: 1; ELSE ;




############ Assigning PLCLive from MB[12] #######
#
OBJ: Fi_MB_PLCLive
	 CPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi_MB1_PLCLive
                P2 = Fi_MB2_PLCLive
         CFV:   IF S0||S1||S2 :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi_PLCLive
                P2 = Fi_PLCOK
                P3 = Fi_PLC_CommOK
                P4 = Fi_MB1_PLCLive
                P5 = Fi_MB1_PLCOK
                P6 = Fi_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P7 = Fi_MB2_PLCLive
                P8 = Fi_MB2_PLCOK
                P9 = Fi_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P4; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P7;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P5; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P8;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV2:   P3 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P6; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P9;  ELSE 0;


############ Assigning MB channel[12] Enable #######
#
OBJ: Fi_MB_Enable
	 CPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi_MB_Enable
         CFV:   IF S0||S1 :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi_MB_Enable
                P2 = Fi_MB1_Enable
                P3 = Fi_MB2_Enable
	 OFV0:   P2 = IF P2 != (P1 && (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2)) : (P1 && (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2)); ELSE;
	 OFV1:   P3 = IF P3 != (P1 && (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1)) : (P1 && (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1)); ELSE;

#####################################################################
#
# Change detection signals
#
# If a change signal is written, the trigger is incremented.
# If the MODBUS+ reads the corresponding table, it will be decremented.

OBJ: Fi_ChangeCount000
    CPAR:
        P0 = Fi_ChangeS000
        P1 = Fi_ChDtAck000
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
        P0 = Fi_ChangeS000
        P1 = Fi_ChDtAck000
        P2 = Fi_ChDtTrg000
    OFV0: P2 = IF S0 && P0 : P2+1;IF S1 && (P2>0) : P2-1; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi_ChangeCount001

    CPAR:

            P0=Fi_StationCtrWrd

    CFV: ELSE Q1;

	OPAR:

            P1=Fi_StationCtrWrd
            P2=Fi_StaProt152

        OFV0:   P0 = IF (S1 & 0x03) && (P1 & 0x01) : 0; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi_Analog
    CPAR:
        P0 =  Fi_TT753____CtWdSet1
        P1 =  Fi_TT753____CtWdSet2
        P2 =  Fi_TT753____MinRaw
        P3 =  Fi_TT753____MaxRaw
        P4 =  Fi_TT753____MinEU
        P5 =  Fi_TT753____MaxEU
        P6 =  Fi_TT753____Raw
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
        P0  = Fi_TT753____CtWdSet1
        P1  = Fi_TT753____CtWdSet2
        P2  = Fi_TT753____CtWd
        P3  = Fi_TT753____CtWdSend
        P4  = Fi_TT753____MinRaw
        P5  = Fi_TT753____MaxRaw
        P6  = Fi_TT753____MinEU
        P7  = Fi_TT753____MaxEU
        P8  = Fi_TT753____ScaleWid
        P9  = Fi_TT753____Raw
        P10 = Fi_TT753____Vl
        P11 = Fi_TT753____Percent
        P12 = Fi_ChDtTrg208
        P13 = Fi_TT753____ValTrig
    OFV0: P3  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) && (P0 & 1) : P2 | (1 << ((P0 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV1: P3  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) && !(P0 & 1) : P2 & ~(1 << ((P0 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV2: P3  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) && (P1 & 1) : P2 | (1 << ((P1 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV3: P3  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) && !(P1 & 1) : P2 & ~(1 << ((P1 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV4: P8  = IF ((S6 | S7) & 03 ) == 3 : ABS(P7-P6); ELSE ;
    OFV5: P10 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7 | S9) & 03) == 3 : P6+(P9-P4)*(P7-P6)/(P5-P4); ELSE ;
    OFV6: P11 = IF (S9 & 03) == 3 : (P9-P4)*100/(P5-P4); ELSE ;
    OFV7: P12 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7) & 03) == 3 : 1; ELSE ;
    OFV8: P13 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7) & 03) == 3 : 1; ELSE ;

#z 2013.07.02 resetting oprator manipulated variables
#z     OFV9:  P0  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) : 0 ; ELSE ;
#z     OFV10: P1  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) : 0 ; ELSE ;

        P0 =  Fi_GF811___CtrWrdEng
        P1 =  Fi_GF811___CtrWrd
    OFV0: P1  = IF (P0 != 0) : P0 ; ELSE ;
    OFV1: P0  = IF (P0 != 0) : 0  ; ELSE ;

#####################################################################
#
#/@ AutroSafe Fire Detector Indicator Status from bits
# I use the MSB for both MSB and LSB status
#

OBJ: Fi_FASStW000MSB
    CPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW000B01
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW000B02
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW000B03
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW000B04
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW000B05
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW000B06
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW000B07
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW000B08
      CFV: ELSE Q1;
      OPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW000B01
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW000B02
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW000B03
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW000B04
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW000B05
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW000B06
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW000B07
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW000B08
            P8 =Fi_FASStW000MSB
    OFV0: P8 = ELSE (P0<<15)|(P1<<14)|(P2<<13)|(P3<<12)|(P4<<11)|(P5<<10)|(P6<<9)|(P7<<8) ;

OBJ: Fi_FASStW000LSB
    CPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW000B09
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW000B10
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW000B11
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW000B12
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW000B13
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW000B14
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW000B15
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW000B16
      CFV: ELSE Q1;
      OPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW000B09
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW000B10
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW000B11
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW000B12
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW000B13
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW000B14
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW000B15
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW000B16
            P8 =Fi_FASStW000LSB
    OFV0: P8 = ELSE (P0<<15)|(P1<<14)|(P2<<13)|(P3<<12)|(P4<<11)|(P5<<10)|(P6<<9)|(P7<<8) ;

            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW053B03
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW053B04
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW053B05
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW053B06
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW053B07
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW053B08
      CFV: ELSE Q1;
      OPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW053B01
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW053B02
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW053B03
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW053B04
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW053B05
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW053B06
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW053B07
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW053B08
            P8 =Fi_FASStW053MSB
    OFV0: P8 = ELSE (P0<<15)|(P1<<14)|(P2<<13)|(P3<<12)|(P4<<11)|(P5<<10)|(P6<<9)|(P7<<8) ;

OBJ: Fi_FASStW053LSB
    CPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW053B09
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW053B10
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW053B11
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW053B12
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW053B13
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW053B14
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW053B15
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW053B16
      CFV: ELSE Q1;
      OPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW053B09
            P1 =Fi_FASPStaW053B10
            P2 =Fi_FASPStaW053B11
            P3 =Fi_FASPStaW053B12
            P4 =Fi_FASPStaW053B13
            P5 =Fi_FASPStaW053B14
            P6 =Fi_FASPStaW053B15
            P7 =Fi_FASPStaW053B16
            P8 =Fi_FASStW053LSB
    OFV0: P8 = ELSE (P0<<15)|(P1<<14)|(P2<<13)|(P3<<12)|(P4<<11)|(P5<<10)|(P6<<9)|(P7<<8) ;

OBJ: Fi_FASStW054MSB
    CPAR:
            P0 =Fi_FASPStaW054B01

#/@ (Fi2_xx)

##############################################################################


OBJ: Fi2_PLC_Popup_02
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi2_AStEvMs212
   CFV:  IF S0&3 : Q1; ELSE Q0;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Popup_02
      P1 = Fi2_AStEvMs212
   OFV0:   P0 = ELSE P1;


OBJ: Fi2_PLC_Popup_08
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi2_AStEvMs218
   CFV:  IF S0&3 : Q1; ELSE Q0;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Popup_08
      P1 = Fi2_AStEvMs218
   OFV0:   P0 = ELSE P1;


############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is written but not changed MB1_PLCOK->0 #######
#/@  Communication may be OK but MB1_PLC is not running
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB1_PLCOK
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi2_MB1_PLCLive
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Fi2_MB1_PLCLive
      P1 = Fi2_MB1_PLCOK
   OFV0:   P1 = IF (S0 & 3) == 3 : 1; IF S0 : 0; ELSE;


############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is not changing in 10 s MB1_PLC_CommOK->0 #######
#   Communication with MB1_PLC wrong
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB1_PLC_CommOK
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 10)== 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB1_PLCLive
                P1 = Fi2_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi2_MB1_PLCLivePrev
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 != P2) : 1;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = ELSE P0;



############ If MB2_PLCLive signal is written but not changed MB2_PLCOK->0 #######
#/@  Communication may be OK but MB2_PLC is not running
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB2_PLCOK
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi2_MB2_PLCLive
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Fi2_MB2_PLCLive
      P1 = Fi2_MB2_PLCOK
   OFV0:   P1 = IF (S0 & 3) == 3 : 1; IF S0 : 0; ELSE;


############ If MB2_PLCLive signal is not changing in 10 s MB2_PLC_CommOK->0 #######
#   Communication with MB2_PLC wrong
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 10)== 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB2_PLCLive
                P1 = Fi2_MB2_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi2_MB2_PLCLivePrev
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 != P2) : 1;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = ELSE P0;

	 
############ MB channel failover #######
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB_FailOver
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 4)== 1) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi2_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi2_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 OFV0:   P0 = IF P1 && (P0 == -1 || P0 == -2 || P0 == 1) : 1;  IF P2 && (P0 == -1 || P0 == -2 || P0 == 2) : 2;  IF !P1 && (P0 == 1) : -2;  IF !P2 && (P0 == 2) : -1;  ELSE;
	 OFV1:   P0 = IF P0 == 0: 1; ELSE ;



	 
############ Assigning PLCLive from MB[12] #######
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB_PLCLive
	 CPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi2_MB1_PLCLive
                P2 = Fi2_MB2_PLCLive
         CFV:   IF S0||S1||S2 :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi2_PLCLive
                P2 = Fi2_PLCOK
                P3 = Fi2_PLC_CommOK
                P4 = Fi2_MB1_PLCLive
                P5 = Fi2_MB1_PLCOK
                P6 = Fi2_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P7 = Fi2_MB2_PLCLive
                P8 = Fi2_MB2_PLCOK
                P9 = Fi2_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P4; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P7;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P5; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P8;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV2:   P3 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P6; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P9;  ELSE 0;
	 	 

		 
		 
############ Assigning MB channel[12] Enable #######
#
OBJ: Fi2_MB_Enable
	 CPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi2_MB_Enable
         CFV:   IF S0||S1 :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi2_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi2_MB_Enable
                P2 = Fi2_MB1_Enable
                P3 = Fi2_MB2_Enable
	 OFV0:   P2 = IF P2 != (P1 && (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2)) : (P1 && (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2)); ELSE;
	 OFV1:   P3 = IF P3 != (P1 && (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1)) : (P1 && (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1)); ELSE;

#####################################################################
#
# Change detection signals
#
# If a change signal is written, the trigger is incremented.
# If the MODBUS+ reads the corresponding table, it will be decremented.

OBJ: Fi2_ChangeCount000
    CPAR:
        P0 = Fi2_ChangeS000
        P1 = Fi2_ChDtAck000
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
        P0 = Fi2_ChangeS000
        P1 = Fi2_ChDtAck000
        P2 = Fi2_ChDtTrg000

    OFV0:   P0 = IF (!P2&!P3&!P4&!P5&!P6&!P7&!P8&!P9& \
                !P10&!P11&!P12&!P13&!P14&!P15&!P16&!P17) : 0; ELSE 1;
    OFV1:   P1 = IF (!P2&!P3&!P4&!P5&!P6&!P7&!P8&!P9& \

    OFV0: P1 = IF (P0 & 0x0800): -(((P0 & 0x0FFF) ^ 0x0FFF)+1); ELSE P0 & 0x0FFF;

#/@ mk_an_math: analog math1

OBJ: Fi2_Analog
    CPAR:
        P0 =  Fi2_TT713401_CtWdSet1
        P1 =  Fi2_TT713401_CtWdSet2
        P2 =  Fi2_TT713401_MinRaw
        P3 =  Fi2_TT713401_MaxRaw
        P4 =  Fi2_TT713401_MinEU
        P5 =  Fi2_TT713401_MaxEU
        P6 =  Fi2_TT713401_Raw
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
        P0  = Fi2_TT713401_CtWdSet1
        P1  = Fi2_TT713401_CtWdSet2
        P2  = Fi2_TT713401_CtWd
        P3  = Fi2_TT713401_CtWdSend
        P4  = Fi2_TT713401_MinRaw
        P5  = Fi2_TT713401_MaxRaw
        P6  = Fi2_TT713401_MinEU
        P7  = Fi2_TT713401_MaxEU
        P8  = Fi2_TT713401_ScaleWid
        P9  = Fi2_TT713401_Raw
        P10 = Fi2_TT713401_Vl
        P11 = Fi2_TT713401_Percent
        P12 = Fi2_ChDtTrg208
        P13 = Fi2_TT713401_ValTrig
    OFV0: P3  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) && (P0 & 1) : P2 | (1 << ((P0 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV1: P3  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) && !(P0 & 1) : P2 & ~(1 << ((P0 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV2: P3  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) && (P1 & 1) : P2 | (1 << ((P1 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV3: P3  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) && !(P1 & 1) : P2 & ~(1 << ((P1 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV4: P8  = IF ((S6 | S7) & 03 ) == 3 : ABS(P7-P6); ELSE ;
    OFV5: P10 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7 | S9) & 03) == 3 : P6+(P9-P4)*(P7-P6)/(P5-P4); ELSE ;
    OFV6: P11 = IF (S9 & 03) == 3 : (P9-P4)*100/(P5-P4); ELSE ;
    OFV7: P12 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7) & 03) == 3 : 1; ELSE ;
    OFV8: P13 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7) & 03) == 3 : 1; ELSE ;

#z 2013.07.02 resetting oprator manipulated variables
#z     OFV9:  P0  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) : 0 ; ELSE ;
#z     OFV10: P1  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) : 0 ; ELSE ;

###############################################################################
#
#/@ (Fi3_xx)
#
##############################################################################

OBJ: Fi3_PLC_Popup_09
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi3_AStEvMs120
   CFV:  IF S0&3 : Q1; ELSE Q0;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Popup_09
      P1 = Fi3_AStEvMs120
   OFV0:   P0 = ELSE P1;



############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is written but not changed MB1_PLCOK->0 #######
#/@  Communication may be OK but MB1_PLC is not running
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB1_PLCOK
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi3_MB1_PLCLive
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Fi3_MB1_PLCLive
      P1 = Fi3_MB1_PLCOK
   OFV0:   P1 = IF (S0 & 3) == 3 : 1; IF S0 : 0; ELSE;


############ If MB1_PLCLive signal is not changing in 10 s MB1_PLC_CommOK->0 #######
#   Communication with MB1_PLC wrong
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB1_PLC_CommOK
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 10)== 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB1_PLCLive
                P1 = Fi3_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi3_MB1_PLCLivePrev
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 != P2) : 1;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = ELSE P0;



############ If MB2_PLCLive signal is written but not changed MB2_PLCOK->0 #######
#/@  Communication may be OK but MB2_PLC is not running
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB2_PLCOK
   CPAR:
      P0 = Fi3_MB2_PLCLive
   CFV:   ELSE Q1;
   OPAR:
      P0 = Fi3_MB2_PLCLive
      P1 = Fi3_MB2_PLCOK
   OFV0:   P1 = IF (S0 & 3) == 3 : 1; IF S0 : 0; ELSE;


############ If MB2_PLCLive signal is not changing in 10 s MB2_PLC_CommOK->0 #######
#   Communication with MB2_PLC wrong
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 10)== 5) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB2_PLCLive
                P1 = Fi3_MB2_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi3_MB2_PLCLivePrev
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 != P2) : 1;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = ELSE P0;



############ MB channel failover #######
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB_FailOver
	 CPAR:
                P0 = SysClkSec
         CFV:   IF ((S0 & 3)==3) && ((P0 % 4)== 1) :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi3_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P2 = Fi3_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 OFV0:   P0 = IF P1 && (P0 == -1 || P0 == -2 || P0 == 1) : 1;  IF P2 && (P0 == -1 || P0 == -2 || P0 == 2) : 2;  IF !P1 && (P0 == 1) : -2;  IF !P2 && (P0 == 2) : -1;  ELSE;
	 OFV1:   P0 = IF P0 == 0: 1; ELSE ;



	 
############ Assigning PLCLive from MB[12] #######
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB_PLCLive
	 CPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi3_MB1_PLCLive
                P2 = Fi3_MB2_PLCLive
         CFV:   IF S0||S1||S2 :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi3_PLCLive
                P2 = Fi3_PLCOK
                P3 = Fi3_PLC_CommOK
                P4 = Fi3_MB1_PLCLive
                P5 = Fi3_MB1_PLCOK
                P6 = Fi3_MB1_PLC_CommOK
                P7 = Fi3_MB2_PLCLive
                P8 = Fi3_MB2_PLCOK
                P9 = Fi3_MB2_PLC_CommOK
	 OFV0:   P1 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P4; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P7;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV1:   P2 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P5; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P8;  ELSE 0;
	 OFV2:   P3 = IF (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2) : P6; IF (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1) : P9;  ELSE 0;
	 	 
	 

	 
############ Assigning MB channel[12] Enable #######
#
OBJ: Fi3_MB_Enable
	 CPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi3_MB_Enable
         CFV:   IF S0||S1 :Q1; ELSE Q0;
	 OPAR:
                P0 = Fi3_MB_FailOver
                P1 = Fi3_MB_Enable
                P2 = Fi3_MB1_Enable
                P3 = Fi3_MB2_Enable
	 OFV0:   P2 = IF P2 != (P1 && (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2)) : (P1 && (P0 == 1 || P0 == -2)); ELSE;
	 OFV1:   P3 = IF P3 != (P1 && (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1)) : (P1 && (P0 == 2 || P0 == -1)); ELSE;

#/@ Change detection signals

#
# Case the init process we read the change tables as well
#

OBJ: Fi3_SimulateChange
    CPAR:
        P0 = Q_Ch17ChainInit
    CFV: IF (S0 && !P0) : Q1;ELSE Q0;
    OPAR:
        P0   = Fi3_ChDtTrg096
        P1   = Fi3_ChDtTrg097
        P2   = Fi3_ChDtTrg098
        P3   = Fi3_ChDtTrg099
        P4   = Fi3_ChDtTrg100
        P5   = Fi3_ChDtTrg101
        P6   = Fi3_ChDtTrg102
        P7   = Fi3_ChDtTrg103
        P8   = Fi3_ChDtTrg104
        P9   = Fi3_ChDtTrg105
        P10  = Fi3_ChDtTrg106
        P11  = Fi3_ChDtTrg107
        P12  = Fi3_ChDtTrg108
        P13  = Fi3_ChDtTrg109
        P14  = Fi3_ChDtTrg110
        P15  = Fi3_ChDtTrg111
        P16  = Fi3_ChDtTrg112
        P17  = Fi3_ChDtTrg113
        P18  = Fi3_ChDtTrg114
        P19  = Fi3_ChDtTrg115
        P20  = Fi3_ChDtTrg116
        P21  = Fi3_ChDtTrg117
        P22  = Fi3_ChDtTrg118
        P23  = Fi3_ChDtTrg119
        P24  = Fi3_ChDtTrg120

#####################################################################
#
# Change detection signals
#
# If a change signal is written, the trigger is incremented.
# If the MODBUS+ reads the corresponding table, it will be decremented.

OBJ: Fi3_ChangeCount000
    CPAR:
        P0 = Fi3_ChangeS000
        P1 = Fi3_ChDtAck000
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
        P0 = Fi3_ChangeS000
        P1 = Fi3_ChDtAck000
        P2 = Fi3_ChDtTrg000
    OFV0: P2 = IF S0 && P0 : P2+1;IF S1 && (P2>0) : P2-1; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi3_ChangeCount001

#####################################################################
#/@ Fire sirena popup and sound_trig

OBJ: Fi3_sirena
    CPAR:   P0 =Fi3_StaProt000
            P1 =Fi3_StaProt001
            P2 =Fi3_StaProt002
            P3 =Fi3_StaProt003
            P4 =Fi3_StaProt005
            P5 =Fi3_StaProt006
            P6 =Fi3_StaProt007
            P7 =Fi3_StaProt009
            P8 =Fi3_StaProt010
            P9 =Fi3_StaProt011
            P10=Fi3_StaProt012
            P11=Fi3_StaProt013

            P12=Fi3_StaProt016
            P13=Fi3_StaProt017
            P14=Fi3_StaProt018
            P15=Fi3_StaProt019

            P16=Fi3_StaProt024
            P17=Fi3_StaProt025
            P18=Fi3_StaProt026

            P19=Fi3_StaProt028
            P20=Fi3_StaProt029
            P21=Fi3_StaProt030
            P22=Fi3_StaProt031


      CFV: ELSE Q1;

      OPAR:
            P0 =Popup_06
            P1 =SOUND_TRIG
            P2 =Fi3_StaProt000
            P3 =Fi3_StaProt001
            P4 =Fi3_StaProt002
            P5 =Fi3_StaProt003
            P6 =Fi3_StaProt005
            P7 =Fi3_StaProt006
            P8 =Fi3_StaProt007
            P9 =Fi3_StaProt009
            P10=Fi3_StaProt010
            P11=Fi3_StaProt011
            P12=Fi3_StaProt012
            P13=Fi3_StaProt013

            P14=Fi3_StaProt016
            P15=Fi3_StaProt017
            P16=Fi3_StaProt018
            P17=Fi3_StaProt019

            P18=Fi3_StaProt024
            P19=Fi3_StaProt025
            P20=Fi3_StaProt026

            P21=Fi3_StaProt028
            P22=Fi3_StaProt029
            P23=Fi3_StaProt030
            P24=Fi3_StaProt031

    OFV0:   P0 = IF (!P2&!P3&!P4&!P5&!P6&!P7&!P8&!P9& \
                !P10&!P11&!P12&!P13&!P14&!P15&!P16&!P17&!P18&!P19&!P20&!P21&!P22&!P23&!P24) : 0; ELSE 1;
    OFV1:   P1 = IF (!P2&!P3&!P4&!P5&!P6&!P7&!P8&!P9& \
                !P10&!P11&!P12&!P13&!P14&!P15&!P16&!P17&!P18&!P19&!P20&!P21&!P22&!P23&!P24) : 0; ELSE 1;

##z#    CPAR:   P0=Fi3_StaEvMs015

##z#            P1=Fi3_StaEvMs015

#####################################################################
#
#/@ Latching protection signals.
#     Bits of the signal: 0 - prot.signal occured
#             1 - test prot.signal occured
#

OBJ: Fi3_LatchMainStationSignals
    CPAR:
        P0   = Fi3_StaProt000
        P1   = Fi3_StaTPro000
        P2   = Fi3_StaBitLch000
        P3   = Fi3_StaProt001
        P4   = Fi3_StaTPro001
        P5   = Fi3_StaBitLch001
        P6   = Fi3_StaProt002
        P7   = Fi3_StaTPro002
        P8   = Fi3_StaBitLch002
        P9   = Fi3_StaProt003
        P10  = Fi3_StaTPro003
        P11  = Fi3_StaBitLch003
        P12  = Fi3_StaProt004
        P13  = Fi3_StaTPro004
        P14  = Fi3_StaBitLch004
        P15  = Fi3_StaProt005
        P16  = Fi3_StaTPro005
        P17  = Fi3_StaBitLch005
        P18  = Fi3_StaProt006
        P19  = Fi3_StaTPro006
        P20  = Fi3_StaBitLch006
        P21  = Fi3_StaProt007
        P22  = Fi3_StaTPro007
        P23  = Fi3_StaBitLch007
        P24  = Fi3_StaProt008
        P25  = Fi3_StaTPro008
        P26  = Fi3_StaBitLch008
        P27  = Fi3_StaProt009
        P28  = Fi3_StaTPro009
        P29  = Fi3_StaBitLch009
        P30  = Fi3_StaProt010
        P31  = Fi3_StaTPro010
        P32  = Fi3_StaBitLch010
        P33  = Fi3_StaProt011
        P34  = Fi3_StaTPro011
        P35  = Fi3_StaBitLch011
        P36  = Fi3_StaProt012
        P37  = Fi3_StaTPro012
        P38  = Fi3_StaBitLch012
        P39  = Fi3_StaProt013

    OFV248: P746 = IF (S744 & 0x03)==0x03 && P744 : P746 | 0x01;IF (S745 & 0x03)==0x03 && P745 : P746 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV249: P749 = IF (S747 & 0x03)==0x03 && P747 : P749 | 0x01;IF (S748 & 0x03)==0x03 && P748 : P749 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV250: P752 = IF (S750 & 0x03)==0x03 && P750 : P752 | 0x01;IF (S751 & 0x03)==0x03 && P751 : P752 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV251: P755 = IF (S753 & 0x03)==0x03 && P753 : P755 | 0x01;IF (S754 & 0x03)==0x03 && P754 : P755 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV252: P758 = IF (S756 & 0x03)==0x03 && P756 : P758 | 0x01;IF (S757 & 0x03)==0x03 && P757 : P758 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV253: P761 = IF (S759 & 0x03)==0x03 && P759 : P761 | 0x01;IF (S760 & 0x03)==0x03 && P760 : P761 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV254: P764 = IF (S762 & 0x03)==0x03 && P762 : P764 | 0x01;IF (S763 & 0x03)==0x03 && P763 : P764 | 0x02;ELSE;
    OFV255: P767 = IF (S765 & 0x03)==0x03 && P765 : P767 | 0x01;IF (S766 & 0x03)==0x03 && P766 : P767 | 0x02;ELSE;

#
#/@ AutroSafe Fire Detector Indicator Status from bits
# I use the MSB for both MSB and LSB status
#

OBJ: Fi3_FASStW000MSB
    CPAR:
            P0 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B01
            P1 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B02
            P2 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B03
            P3 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B04
            P4 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B05
            P5 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B06
            P6 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B07
            P7 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B08
      CFV: ELSE Q1;
      OPAR:
            P0 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B01
            P1 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B02
            P2 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B03
            P3 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B04
            P4 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B05
            P5 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B06
            P6 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B07
            P7 =Fi3_FASPStaW000B08
            P8 =Fi3_FASStW000MSB
    OFV0: P8 = ELSE (P0<<15)|(P1<<14)|(P2<<13)|(P3<<12)|(P4<<11)|(P5<<10)|(P6<<9)|(P7<<8) ;

#/@ mk_an_math: analog math1

OBJ: Fi3_Analog
    CPAR:
        P0 =  Fi3_PT708_CtWdSet1
        P1 =  Fi3_PT708_CtWdSet2
        P2 =  Fi3_PT708_MinRaw
        P3 =  Fi3_PT708_MaxRaw
        P4 =  Fi3_PT708_MinEU
        P5 =  Fi3_PT708_MaxEU
        P6 =  Fi3_PT708_Raw
    CFV: ELSE Q1;
    OPAR:
        P0  = Fi3_PT708_CtWdSet1
        P1  = Fi3_PT708_CtWdSet2
        P2  = Fi3_PT708_CtWd
        P3  = Fi3_PT708_CtWdSend
        P4  = Fi3_PT708_MinRaw
        P5  = Fi3_PT708_MaxRaw
        P6  = Fi3_PT708_MinEU
        P7  = Fi3_PT708_MaxEU
        P8  = Fi3_PT708_ScaleWid
        P9  = Fi3_PT708_Raw
        P10 = Fi3_PT708_Vl
        P11 = Fi3_PT708_Percent
        P12 = Fi3_ChDtTrg208
        P13 = Fi3_PT708_ValTrig
    OFV0: P3  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) && (P0 & 1) : P2 | (1 << ((P0 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV1: P3  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) && !(P0 & 1) : P2 & ~(1 << ((P0 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV2: P3  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) && (P1 & 1) : P2 | (1 << ((P1 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV3: P3  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) && !(P1 & 1) : P2 & ~(1 << ((P1 >> 1)-1)) ; ELSE ;
    OFV4: P8  = IF ((S6 | S7) & 03 ) == 3 : ABS(P7-P6); ELSE ;
    OFV5: P10 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7 | S9) & 03) == 3 : P6+(P9-P4)*(P7-P6)/(P5-P4); ELSE ;
    OFV6: P11 = IF (S9 & 03) == 3 : (P9-P4)*100/(P5-P4); ELSE ;
    OFV7: P12 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7) & 03) == 3 : 1; ELSE ;
    OFV8: P13 = IF ((S4 | S5 | S6 | S7) & 03) == 3 : 1; ELSE ;

#z 2013.07.02 resetting oprator manipulated variables
#z     OFV9:  P0  = IF S0 && (P0 != 0) : 0 ; ELSE ;
#z     OFV10: P1  = IF S1 && (P1 != 0) : 0 ; ELSE ;

OBJ: Fi3_Analog
    CPAR:
        P0 =  Fi3_PT709_CtWdSet1
        P1 =  Fi3_PT709_CtWdSet2
        P2 =  Fi3_PT709_MinRaw
